          <p>Web pages with bad certificates displayed as blank</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Users could no longer send using smtp-relay.gmail.com</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Changing to new drafts folder and then back did not correctly restore the folder</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

