        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Drag-drop of unselected contact inserted wrong or no email address</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Thunderbird could crash on startup</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Adding an account could fail and cause UI hang</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

