        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Delete or detach attachments did not work for some IMAP servers</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Saving a new draft retained superceded version</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Language field in settings was empty after restart in Troubleshoot Mode</p>
          
