  <entry>
    <id>https://www.thunderbird.net/en-US/thunderbird/142.0/releasenotes/</id>
    <title type="html">Thunderbird 142.0</title>
    <author>
      <name>Thunderbird</name>
      <uri>https://www.thunderbird.net</uri>
    </author>
    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.thunderbird.net/en-US/thunderbird/142.0/releasenotes/"/>
    <updated>2025-08-19T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <published>2025-08-19T00:00:00+00:00</published>

    <content type="html"><![CDATA[
      

  
  

  
    

    
      
        
        

        
          <h3>What’s New</h3>
        

        
        
          <ul>
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Visual signatures can be added to PDF attachments opened in Thunderbird</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>'Copy Message Link' and 'Copy News Link' added to header pane 'More actions'</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Folder copy enabled within mail server accounts and local folders</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>'Reset Folder Order' option added to folder pane to reset custom folder sorting</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        
          </ul>
        

        
          <h3>Changed</h3>
        

        
        
          <ul>
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>'Copy Message Location' removed from mail context menu</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        
          </ul>
        

        
          <h3>Fixed</h3>
        

        
        
          <ul>
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Users with attachments open in tabs saw an error on Thunderbird restart</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Notification sounds did not respect operating system's do-not-disturb mode</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Non-English localized Thunderbird created English special folders on first start</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Users were unable to use Fastmail calendars due to missing OAuth settings</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Sending from unified or local folder failed if no default account was set</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Right-clicking 'List-ID' -&gt; 'Unsubscribe' created double encoded draft subject</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>On Linux, the close caption button was inactive when mouse was in screen corner</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Toggling dark message mode did not restore focus and scroll position</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Message list scrolled back when returning to mail tab after opening a message</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Deleting a single message in folder using 'Group by Sort' failed after CTRL+A</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>New newsgroups were not added in alphabetical order by default</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>After updating to version 142, all newsgroup folders were sorted alphabetically</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>With Thunderbird closed, clicking a 'mailto:' link to send signed message failed</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Replying could fail with <code>mailnews.reply_quoting_selection.multi_word</code> set false</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Multiple saves while using 'Options' -&gt; 'Send a Copy' resulted in multiple copies</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Thunderbird did not display contact photos in WebP format from CardDAV servers</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Installations from Microsoft Store did not open when clicking 'mailto:' links</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Clicking the backspace icon in the quick filter field cleared the input field</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Initial launch had long load times and UI lag while messages downloaded</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>'Mark' -&gt; 'All Read' affected newsgroup messages that had not been fetched yet</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Thunderbird could not reconnect to newsgroups after connection loss until restarted</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Sending a newsgroup post appeared successful when it had actually failed</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Archived RSS feed messages were sent to the archive folder of default identity</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Opening Website header link in RSS feed incorrectly re-encoded URL parameters</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Visual and UX improvements</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p><a href="https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/security/known-vulnerabilities/thunderbird/#thunderbird142">Security fixes</a></p>
          
        </li>
      
    
    </ul>
  
  

<p>As always, you’re encouraged to <a href="https://connect.mozilla.org/t5/ideas/idb-p/ideas/label-name/thunderbird">tell us what you think</a>, <a href="https://support.mozilla.org/questions/new/thunderbird">ask for help</a>, or <a href="https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/enter_bug.cgi?product=Thunderbird">file a bug in Bugzilla</a></p>
<style> li p { display: inline; } </style>
      ]]>
    </content>
  </entry>
  
